<P>Sam &s;incere in all I say to you, and have no Vanity in saying it. Yourcally over value $e greatly in my Poetical Capacity; and I am &s;iere your Work $word$ do me infinitely too much Honour, even if it blamed me of$ener than it com|mended&punc; For the first you will do with $$nity, the last with Exce&s;s $word$ $$uld be glad to pa$d with some &s;hare of any good Man's Admiration, For one of the Affection, and $word$ Relief that I am not wholly undeserving to be $word$ $word$ I am to you, Sir,</P>
