<P>This is quite a Letter of Busine&s;s, and therefore excuse it, I will not mix in i$ a Word of Affection, which I have not a Moment's time to expre&s;s, and will not prejudice the sacred Idea of Friend&s;hip.</P>
<P>It is near a Month age that I try'd to see W. Thom&s;on, to know the Time of his Tragedy: He was not within my Reach; and therefore at last I wrote to him, and also to W. M&mdash;, to let them both know the Deference you paid them, and the Her$i$ (I will not call it le&s;s) Disinterestedne&s;s you expre&s;s'd in regard to them I have not $word$ been able to $word$ where they are, $r any way to have an $word$ further, than I have learn'd it will be imp$&s;sible, for either of them to bring $word$ their $word$ early (a Friend of $he$$$ $$lling m$ they are in no forwardn$$$) $ill th$ Middle $word$ of $in$$r; therefore you m$y have r$$m. I wish from my S$$l you may get yours first, as well ac$ed as i$ de$$$$es. A better, that may ec$$pse i$, or $word$ $$rthily, follow i$, I $span$ to &s;ec.&mdash;But $$o$ this No$i$e&punc; I believe you may safely advance i$, the $word$ the better.</P>
<P>My Lord $word$ is $word$ with me, $$re properly I $e$ belong to him, Body as $word$ as Mind (for my Mind is every where his). I would to God you had any Op|pertunity of seeing as&mdash;before $e parts my House &s;hould be yours, as much of i$ $$is not his. I believe I &s;hall seen go with him on a little Journey before h$ quits England. You'll forgive the $word$ Con$$usion of this, yet it may tell you all the $$ngest and $$st written Letter could tell you, that I am very &s;incerely</P>
